item.title: Scavenger Hunt
item.description: Scavenger Hunt - Hint 1 (NOT USED) ![Scavenger Hunt Challenge Hint 1](/images/patriotctf_2023/Scavenger_Hunt_Hint_1.jpg) Scavenger Hunt - Hint 2 (NOT USED) ![Scavenger Hunt Challenge Hint 2](/images/patriotctf_2023/Scavenger_Hunt_Hint_2.jpg) Write-Up Opened up the Terminal and ran dirb command on the website: dirb http://chal.pctf.competitivecyber.club:5999 Scan results provided the following 2 URLs: /index.html (main website) /robots.txt (file located on website) Opened up Burpsuite and used Proxy browser with Interceptor turned on. Entered URL listed on the challenge page.
